===Etymology 1===
From the {{bor|en|cmn-pinyin|-}} romanization of the {{bor|en|cmn|-}} Chinese pronunciation for {{zh-l|新疆|new territory, new frontier}}, from {{zh-l|新|new}} + {{zh-l|疆|territory, border, frontier}}.
