* {{q|from [[Wade-Giles]]}} {{l|en|Hsin-chiang}}, {{l|en|Hsinchiang}}
* {{l|en|Hsin-kiang}}
* {{l|en|Sinkiang}}
* {{q|misspelling}} {{l|en|Xingjiang}}
